creator: Zenbly
descriptionHtml:
We make managing your health, fitness and wellbeing routine easy and enjoyable. Whether it’s booking your favourite classes, check in when you arrive, paying with your app, managing your membership or communicating to friends, staff and trainers, you can do it all on the go!



Group class schedule

Easily see when your favourite classes are running and reserve your spot in the class. Easily track your attendance history to ensure you are keeping on track and making the most of your membership.



Find a Personal Trainer

View trainer profiles and at your health facility and match the best fit for you. Book in though the app and schedule a training session or consultation.



Manage my purchases

Make purchases through the app and view/update your membership details with ease. Our app allows you to manage and ensure you are on the best membership option for your needs.



Connect

Connect and stay in touch with those at your health facility.



Notifications

Receive reminders and keep up to date with current events and updates.



My Results

Track your progression and see the benefits of exercise. Stay motivated by easily seeing were you started and were you have progressed to
Cheers
